<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The best way to get Faldor to spawn is this. First go to Crow's and camp in the back room. make another char in Kaladim. with this new char go to Dagnor's Cauldorn and find the little camp with the four NPC's. you will find Faldor's Brother there. just pop the question. "Where is Faldor Hendry?". He will tell you where he is but pay no attention to this. Log off and back on with your real char at Qey. I timed it and he spawned within 25 mins. you know the rest. He is around 24 lvl. easy kill for a lvl 27.<BR>
my two copper<BR>
