<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The first part of the quest is to kill the clockwork rat ( a rare spawn in the mines of Kaladim )  You will have to kill the place holder giant rats and diseased rats as they spawn in the mines to get the clockwork to eventually spawn.  When the clockwork spawns, kill it and take the parts to Beno this will get you the letter and begin the quest.  <BR>
