<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Malder of Tunare</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-30 19:01:51</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am working on this quest for the second time now.  It's a pretty easy quest for a 23 bard, although I've spent many hours waiting for faldor hendrys.  I have made several characters and sent them to Dagnors Cauldron and talked to his brother, then camped and relogged with my bard and waited and waited.  The first time he spawned it took 8 hours, and he still has yet to spawn a second time.  I have spent over 5 hours on 4 seperate occasions waiting for his next spawn, and still nothing (I already sold the first axe).  I did talk to a GM one night when I was extremely frustrated and he said that Faldor was a rare spawn, and didn't have a triggered spawn.<BR>
<BR>
Just my 2cp</font></td></tr></table>
